    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint condition and presents exactly like it just rolled off the showroom floor. The exterior paint is flawless with a deep, mirror-like shine and no imperfections, while the interior remains in pristine state with no signs of wear. Mechanically, the car is perfect, having been meticulously maintained and kept in a climate-controlled environment. This is a rare opportunity for a collector or a discerning buyer to own a vehicle that has been preserved in showroom-new condition.",
